original_title: Musikladen Live: The Very Best of ABBA
overview: Comprising of two Musikladen performances (1976 and 1979), The Best of ABBA is a showcase for arguably the greatest musical group to hail from Sweden. Highlights: "Waterloo," "Dancing Queen," S.O.S.," Honey Honey" and more!
title: Musikladen Live: The Very Best of ABBA
